# Premium Taxi Landing Page Walkthrough

I have successfully built the premium landing page for your taxi/transfer service using React, Vite, Tailwind CSS (v3 for stability), and Framer Motion. 

## Changes Made

1. **Project Setup**: Initialized a Vite React application in the `TAXI` folder.
28. **Styling & Theming (Dark Theme Restoration)**: Transitioned back to the original elegant **Dark Theme** to maintain a premium, moody aesthetic.
    - **Color Palette**: Reverted [tailwind.config.js](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/tailwind.config.js) with dark variants (`primary-dark`, `surface`) and pure white text, while preserving the vibrant `accent` (amber/orange) and `emerald` (green) for calls to action.
    - **Global Layout**: [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/App.jsx) now uses `bg-primary-dark` and `text-slate-300`.
3. **Components Refactored for Dark Theme**:
    - [Header.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/Header.jsx): Reverted to a dark semi-transparent background with white text. Restored the contrast for the Taxi logo and dark mobile menu styling.
    - [Hero.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/Hero.jsx): Restored the dark overlay overlaying the car image to a `bg-primary-dark/80` gradient. Swapped dark text back to white/slate. Updated both the complex desktop glassmorphism form and the simpler mobile form to use dark surface backgrounds with light text inputs. Changed the booking buttons to an emerald green color (`bg-emerald-600`), and updated the desktop button text to **"ЗАФИКСИРОВАТЬ ЦЕНУ И АВТО"** while the mobile buttons text remains **"РАССЧИТАТЬ СТОИМОСТЬ"**. Additionally, the "Популярные направления" marquee has been scaled down and embedded directly below the booking forms for a more cohesive layout.
    - [Trust.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/Trust.jsx): Switched the container back to a dark surface background (`bg-surface`) and cards to `bg-primary-dark` with ambient orange shadows on hover.
    - [RoutesPreview.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/RoutesPreview.jsx): This standalone section was removed from the home page, as its content (the marquee) was integrated into [Hero.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/Hero.jsx).
    - [Services.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/Services.jsx) (Fleet): The carousel background is now `bg-[#0f141f]`. Car cards use a dark layout with soft borders and light text.
    - [Masters.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/Masters.jsx): Updated from white cards back to dark gradient backgrounds (`bg-primary-dark`) with glowing orange shadow effects. **Added actual driver profile photos** to replace the previous generic initial-based icons.
    - [Reviews.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/Reviews.jsx): Switched to a dark background (`bg-[#0f141f]`) and dark review cards, ensuring the text remains legible against the premium dark mode. **Added passenger profile photos** to replace the previous initial-based icons.
    - [CtaForm.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/CtaForm.jsx): Refactored to feature a stark dark layout (`bg-primary-dark`) with a sophisticated gradient panel, restoring the high-end appeal.
4. **Assembly**: All dark theme components coalesce into a seamless, mobile-responsive single-page application.
5. **SEO Enhancements**: Added a new rich text block ([SeoBlock.jsx](file:///c:/Users/baben/Desktop/TAXI/src/components/SeoBlock.jsx)) at the bottom of the Home page (above the footer) detailing long-distance transfer services, guarantees, and fleet information to improve search engine visibility and user trust.

> [!NOTE]
> The site's original "dark, premium aesthetic" has been completely restored across all sections.

